    - m_Type: 0
      Title:
        m_Untranslated: 
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: "Up until now, you've been selecting the <b>Move</b> and
          <b>Rotate</b> tools from the toolbar. However, Unity offers a quicker way
          to switch between these tools using shortcuts on the top row of your keyboard.
          The shortcuts <b>Q, W, E, R, T,</b> and <b>Y</b> allow you to swiftly flip
          through various tools, with W for the <b>Move</b> tool and E for the <b>Rotate</b>
          tool. \n\nYou're about to use these shortcuts to move and rotate your second
          puzzle piece.\n\nMastering these shortcuts will greatly speed up your workflow,
          but if you\u2019re more comfortable selecting them manually, feel free
          to continue to do that!"
